sequenceDiagram
    participant Controller as KServe Controller
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>S3/GCS/HF<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Server as AutoGluon Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant Predictor as AutoGluon Predictor<br/>(in-process)
    participant Client as Client / KServe Router
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Controller,Server: Flow 1: Model Loading (Startup)
    Controller->>Server: Create Pod with autogluon-server image<br/>ServiceAccount credentials
    Server->>Storage: kserve_storage.Storage.download()<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / storage-config secret
    Storage-->>Server: Model artifacts (TabularPredictor or TimeSeriesPredictor)
    Server->>Server: Auto-detect model type<br/>(try TimeSeriesPredictor, fallback TabularPredictor)
    Server->>Predictor: Load AutoGluon predictor<br/>from local filesystem

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 2: v1 REST Inference
    Client->>Server: POST /v1/models/{model_name}:predict<br/>HTTP/8080, JSON payload
    Server->>Server: Parse v1 JSON request<br/>(instances format)
    Server->>Predictor: TabularPredictor.predict()<br/>or TimeSeriesPredictor.predict()
    Predictor-->>Server: Prediction result (DataFrame)
    Server-->>Client: JSON response<br/>{"predictions": [...]}

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 3: v2 Open Inference Protocol (REST)
    Client->>Server: POST /v2/models/{model_name}/infer<br/>HTTP/8080, tensor payload
    Server->>Server: Map v2 tensors → DataFrame<br/>(feature name resolution, dtype mapping)
    Server->>Predictor: TabularPredictor.predict()<br/>(v2 only for tabular)
    Predictor-->>Server: Prediction result
    Server-->>Client: v2 InferResponse<br/>(tensor format)

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 4: v2 gRPC Inference
    Client->>Server: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/8081, tensor payload
    Server->>Server: Map v2 tensors → DataFrame
    Server->>Predictor: TabularPredictor.predict()
    Predictor-->>Server: Prediction result
    Server-->>Client: ModelInferResponse<br/>(gRPC tensor)

    Note over Prom,Server: Flow 5: Metrics Scrape
    Prom->>Server: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080
    Server-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(preprocess, predict, postprocess,<br/>explain duration histograms)
